description:
-=- Proudly Presents -=-

    Crazy Machines 2: Invaders from Space (Bundle Ed.) (c) Viva Media


Release On   : 16 July 2013         Disk Amount/Format : 1 CD ISO
Type of Game : Puzzle               Media Protection   : Nothing


Kick your brain into high gear with incredible mind bending puzzles. Tinker
with wrecking balls, lightening rods, lasers, pulleys, springs, gears and
more to create the chain reaction you need! Unlock a new 3D world of addictive
fun that the entire family will enjoy! New parts and unique building parts
featuring UFOs, Flinky, the bouncing alien, X-Ray Display and more! Multiple
solutions, play these challenging puzzles again and again Swap ideas with other
members of the online community Trick out your own contraptions in free-style
mode.


Burn/mount, install, play!
